        "#tart with the coefficient of the highest degree (3)\n",
        "[#Multiply by x: 3x Add the next coefficient: 3x + 2 Multiply by x: (3x + 2)x = 3x² + 2x\n",
        "#Add the next coefficient: 3x² + 2x - 5\n",
        "#Multiply by x: (3x² + 2x - 5)x = 3x³ + 2x² - 5x\n",
        "#Add the final coefficient: 3x³ + 2x² - 5x + 7"
